              "free_text": [
                " Outgoing charged particles were",
                "identified using one 140 mum and one 1000 mum Micron",
                "S2 type silicon detectors as a AE+E particle",
                "telescope over an angular range of 33deg to 66deg with",
                "respect to the beam axis."
              ]
            }
          ],
