              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COINC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Coincidences between tritons identified in EdE",
                "telescope and fission fragments detected in additional",
                "Si detector was required to identify the reaction",
                "channel"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Surrogate method was used to measure fission",
                "probability of 238Np produced in 238U(3He,t)238Np",
                "reaction. The measured fission probability was",
                "combined with calculated 237U+n compound nucleus",
                "cross section to obtain 237Np(n,f) fission",
                "cross section."
              ]
            }
          ],
